Matt Peron: Global Earnings Review – Europe Catching Up

 





U.S. earnings growth, despite confusing headlines, is growing at a steady, if not monotonous, 4%-5%. Meanwhile, the earnings picture outside the U.S. is getting more interesting. Matt Peron explains.









